Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Direct frontage to South Pine Road

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Site Credentials:
- 1,250sqm GFA including warehouse, office and showroom
- Direct frontage and signage to South Pine Road
- Minimum clearance 7.5metres
- Internal male and female amenities 
- NBN available to the site
- 3 phase power throughout 
- Mulitple container height roller doors being 6.7m & 5m wide respectively 
- Massive cantilevered awnings over all doors for all weather loading
- Allocated on-site car parking including allocation of under-croft bays
- On site designated container set down areas

Location Credentials: 
- Brendale is centrally located in North Brisbane
- Established business hub
- 30 mins to Brisbane CBD
- 30 mins to Brisbane Airport
- 50 mins to Sunshine Coast
- Good connection to Bruce Highway, Gateway Motorway, Gympie Road & Sandgate Road
- Surrounded by major amenities including Council HQ, Strathpine Regional Shopping Centre
- Strathpine Train Station nearby
 
Available for lease, for further information please contact the exclusive agents CBRE
